Description
===========
A small collection of simple functionObjects that average, integrate 
etc fields in the whole volume or on patches

Original Author
===============
Bernhard Gschaider (bgschaid@ice-sf.at)

Current Maintainer
==================
Bernhard Gschaider (bgschaid@ice-sf.at)

Contributors
============
Bernhard Gschaider: basic integration etc stuff
Hannes Kroeger (hannes@kroegeronline.net): mtv-writer. 

Documentation
=============
See: http://openfoamwiki.net/index.php/Contrib_simpleFunctionObjects

Installation/Compilation
========================

The library can be compiled with "wmake libso". It doesn't have to be
installed in a specific location.

Required OpenFOAM-Version (Known to work with)
==============================================
1.5
There is a different version that works with 1.4.1

History
=======

 - The sampleSurfaceFunctionObject, volumeAverage and patchForces were removed 
   because this functionality is present in 1.5
 - volumeAverage was reintroduced because the average-functionObject in OF 1.5
   does time-averages of complete fields

